name: ZALA DE PERTO
description:
''ZALA DE PERTO'' / ''NEAR ZALA''

A zine that brings together some works and shows, up close, some details that I believe are important in my evolution. The zine details show the paint, oil pastels, spray and the canva, or paper.

TEXT IN ENGLISH ''A zine made for you to look closer at some details of some works that I developed in 2021''

''Now you know all the details. @zala_faz_zalas, 2021''

2021
BY ZALA
